&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.pletscher.org/writings/latex/beamerthemes.php"&gt;http://www.pletscher.org/writings/latex/beamerthemes.php&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Temą nurodyti galima taip:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code latex"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_ed5f15f132bf41499356db5fb53b113e-1" name="rest_code_ed5f15f132bf41499356db5fb53b113e-1" href="https://sirex.lt/posts/2010/kaip-pateiktis-kuria-tikri-vyrai/#rest_code_ed5f15f132bf41499356db5fb53b113e-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;\usetheme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;Malmoe&lt;span class="nb"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
